    <div class="col-md-8">
              <div class="wwf-text--lg-sm wwf-text--xl-lg">
            <div>
        <div class="page-description mb-3"><span>Sadly, there are more tigers in captivity in the US than are left in the wild. Tiger populations have declined by around 95% since the beginning of the 20th century.</span></div>
    </div>

        </div>
                    <div class="wwf-text--lg-sm wwf-text--xl-lg">
          
            <div class="field field-intro-copy"><p><span>Your adoption will help fund tiger protection projects such as movement monitoring and reducing poaching, and will also help fund other vital work around the world. When you choose an animal adoption, you are supporting both your chosen animals as well as wider work to help bring our world back to life.</span></p></div>
      
        </div>
